* --- 1. IC LOGIC (Keep this as it is) ---
* Pin order: STAT VSS VBAT VDD PROG
.subckt MCP73831 STAT VSS VBAT VDD PROG
* Internal logic
R_d1 VDD VSS 10Meg
R_d2 VBAT VSS 10Meg
V_prog PROG VSS DC 1.0
* B_charge current source connected between VDD and VBAT
B_charge VDD VBAT I = 1000 * abs(v(PROG)/2000) * (0.5 * (sgn(4.2 - V(VBAT)) + 1))
.ends MCP73831

* --- 2. EXTERNAL CIRCUIT ---
V1 V_IN 0 5V
C1 V_IN 0 4.7u

* Charging element (Battery model)
C_bat V_BAT 0 1000u
.ic v(V_BAT)=3.7

C2 V_BAT 0 4.7u
R1 V_PROG 0 2k

* Main Block (Mapping: STAT=Dummy, VSS=0, VBAT=V_BAT, VDD=V_IN, PROG=V_PROG)
X1 DUMMY_STAT 0 V_BAT V_IN V_PROG MCP73831

* --- 3. ANALYSIS ---
* 0.05m time step hai aur 20ms total time (2 cycle ke liye)
.tran 0.5m 5m
.control
run

* Plots
plot v(V_IN) title 'Input Voltage (Vin)'
plot v(V_BAT) title 'Battery Charging Voltage (Vbat)'
plot v(V_PROG) title 'Programming Voltage (Vprog)'

.endc
.end